<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased DB Instance Create Times>
We are investigating increased DB instance creation times in the US-WEST-2 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased DB Instance Create Times>
We have identified the problem with increased DB instance creation times in the US-WEST-2 Region and are working towards a resolution.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased DB Instance Create Times>
Between 3:20 PM and 7:05 PM PST, we experienced increased DB instance creation times in the US-WEST-2 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
